    <abstract>
      <t>An IGP Flexible Algorithm (Flex-Algorithm) allows IGP to compute constraint-based paths. The base IGP Flex-Algorithm specification describes how it is used with Segment Routing (SR) data planes - SR MPLS and SRv6. This document extends IGP Flex-Algorithm, so that it can be used with regular IPv4 and IPv6 forwarding.</t>
